<i>noun</i>: 산스크리트어, 梵語, 범어 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>산스크리트어, 梵語, 범어</dt><br>
<dd>an ancient language of India (the language of the Vedas and of Hinduism); an official language of India although it is now used only for religious purposes</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: Sanskrit, Sanskritic language</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
